@startuml
title 嵌入式 Linux 系统到应用基本架构图

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
top to bottom direction

rectangle "应用层 (Application)" as APP #E8F4FF {
  [HMI/业务应用]
  [tcu_logic]
  [tcu_pile_controller]
  [tcu_meter]
  [tcu_comm]
  [logger/daemon]
}

rectangle "中间件与基础库 (Middleware)" as MIDDLE #F3F8E8 {
  [MQTT Broker (mosquitto)]
  [MQTT Client SDK]
  [cJSON]
  [libv2gshm / IPC]
  [配置与日志组件]
}

rectangle "用户空间系统服务 (Userspace)" as USER #FFF7E8 {
  [systemd/init]
  [udev]
  [netif/ssh]
  [诊断与运维工具]
}

rectangle "Linux 内核层 (Kernel)" as KERNEL #FCEEF5 {
  [进程调度]
  [内存管理]
  [VFS]
  [网络协议栈]
  [IPC机制]
}

rectangle "设备驱动层 (Drivers)" as DRV #F8F0FF {
  [CAN/SOCKETCAN]
  [UART/RS485]
  [Ethernet/Wi-Fi]
  [GPIO/Watchdog]
  [Storage/eMMC]
}

rectangle "板级支持包 (BSP)" as BSP #F2F2F2 {
  [设备树 (DTS)]
  [时钟/电源/引脚配置]
  [SoC 外设适配]
}

rectangle "引导链路 (Boot)" as BOOT #EFEFEF {
  [BootROM]
  [SPL/U-Boot]
  [Kernel + DTB + RootFS]
}

rectangle "硬件层 (Hardware)" as HW #EDEDED {
  [ARM SoC]
  [CAN收发器]
  [RS485收发器]
  [网口/4G模块]
  [Flash/eMMC]
}

APP -down-> MIDDLE : API/消息总线
MIDDLE -down-> USER : 系统服务调用
USER -down-> KERNEL : syscall
KERNEL -down-> DRV : 驱动接口
DRV -down-> BSP : 板级适配
BSP -down-> BOOT : 启动参数/设备树
BOOT -down-> HW : 上电启动

note right of APP
本项目业务主链路：
pile_controller / tcu_logic /
tcu_meter / tcu_comm
通过 MQTT 解耦协作
end note

@enduml

